btrplace.solver.choco.duration

Class ActionDurationFromOptionalAttribute<E extends Element>

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.solver.choco.duration.ActionDurationFromOptionalAttribute<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionDurationEvaluator<E>

    public class ActionDurationFromOptionalAttribute<E extends Element>
extends Object
implements ActionDurationEvaluator<E>
    A duration evaluator that try to get a duration from an attribute if exists. Otherwise, it relies on a "parent" evaluator. The retrieved attribute value must be an Integer object.
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
